<section class="how" id="how-it-works">
  <div class="container">

    <p class="section-eyebrow">How it works</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Maïa shows up.<br /><em style="font-style:italic;color:#B0A898">Every. Single. Day.</em></h2>
    <p class="section-subtitle">Connect her to WhatsApp or Slack. She takes care of the rest, whether you like it or not.</p>

    <div class="chat-wrap">

      <div class="chat-day">Monday · 8:47 AM</div>

      <div class="bubble-row from-maia">
        <div class="bubble-avatar"><img src="/avatar.png" alt="Maïa" /></div>
        <div>
          <div class="bubble">Good morning 👋 I picked 3 people who match your ideal early user. <strong>Emails are drafted and ready.</strong> Hit send before you open your IDE. 5 min max.</div>
          <div class="bubble-time">8:47 AM</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bubble-row from-founder">
        <div>
          <div class="bubble">Noted I'll do it after I fix this bug</div>
          <div class="bubble-time">9:03 AM</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="chat-day">Monday · 6:30 PM</div>

      <div class="bubble-row from-maia">
        <div class="bubble-avatar"><img src="/avatar.png" alt="Maïa" /></div>
        <div>
          <div class="bubble">Hey. Still waiting on those DMs. The bug can wait. <strong>Your users can't find you if you don't show up.</strong> 10 minutes. Go.</div>
          <div class="bubble-time">6:30 PM</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bubble-row from-founder">
        <div>
          <div class="bubble">you're kind of annoying you know that</div>
          <div class="bubble-time">6:44 PM</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bubble-row from-maia">
        <div class="bubble-avatar"><img src="/avatar.png" alt="Maïa" /></div>
        <div>
          <div class="bubble">I know. Did you send them?</div>
          <div class="bubble-time">6:44 PM</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bubble-row from-founder">
        <div>
          <div class="bubble">…yes fine done</div>
          <div class="bubble-time">7:02 PM</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="chat-day">Wednesday · 11:20 AM</div>

      <div class="bubble-row from-maia">
        <div class="bubble-avatar"><img src="/avatar.png" alt="Maïa" /></div>
        <div>
          <div class="bubble">One of your DMs got a reply. <strong>That's a warm lead.</strong> Want me to draft a follow-up that doesn't feel pushy?</div>
          <div class="bubble-time">11:20 AM</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bubble-row from-founder">
        <div>
          <div class="bubble">ok ok you were right let's go 🚀</div>
          <div class="bubble-time">11:22 AM</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bubble-row from-maia">
        <div class="bubble-avatar"><img src="/avatar.png" alt="Maïa" /></div>
        <div class="typing-bubble">
          <span></span><span></span><span></span>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="chat-callout">
      <span class="chat-callout-dot"></span>
      Available on WhatsApp &amp; Slack
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
